We Hope This Romantic Song Must Be a Big Hit .

"Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora"
Lyrics:-

Mukhuda:-
**************
M:-
Aji phagunare lagigala ranga
              Sei ranga aji deigala daga

Cross:-
Hrudaya jadi delu tu mate
       De kahile debi mu tate, tope sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(୦)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu 
                 Ajithu mora.....(୦)



Antara:-01
***************
M:-
Piladine gote kahani te sunithili
       Aakasha deshare pari tie thae boli
           Tu sei pari, aji janigali

F:-
Kebe dine gote kabita te padhithili
         Sagara majhire raja tie rahe boli
               Tu sei raja, aji chinhi gali

Cross:-
M:-
Chhatire tate rakhibaa pain
        Sata sagara asichi dein, debi sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(01)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu
                 Ajithu mora.....(01)

Antara:-02
**************
F:-
Dinaku dina mu saja hue beshi kain 
   Aina kahuchi to pari sundari nahi
           Mu bodhe to bata, rahichi chahi

M:-
Aakasha taa aji pruthibi ku chhuindela
      Nijathu nijara kehi jane miligala
            To bata mo bata, gotie hela

Cross:-
F:-
 Manaku gote mana milila
      Aau ja khali baki rahila, tope sindura

Tag:-
M:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(02)
F:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu 
                 Ajithu mora.....(02)

snippet.title: Indians And Exercise | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
Find your meaningful connection on happn : http://gethap.pn/aoHj

This Video shows all the crazy fun things that happens while exercising . Indians and Exercise we all have been there in different phases of our fitness journey incidents like  Single people going to gym , parks for workout , jog and suddenly meeting their love . Great for single guys and single girls for becoming fitness couple . Early morning walks with sister . Siblings going to parks like bonta , doing trekking and hiking , playing badminton . Enjoying healthy lifestyle coconut water with malai , vegetable juice , fruit juices , karela juice , chai tapri , tea and bread pakoda ,  eating neem leaves neem datun . Foodie Aunty going on diet to loose weight , controlling the urge to eating oily sugary atta halwa . Skipping sugar , oil , going on morning walks , avoiding cheat meals . Waking up early the 4 AM club to exercise . 2.0 version of friend she is so dedicated to change her body , workout clothes shopping , having every athletic brand nike addidas , puma , gym tights , sports bra , shoes , running , jogging , stretching and then workout motivation goes down in one day . Aunties Uncles laughing in park , joining free yoga classes . Girls and Girl things and their workout fashion . Yoga teacher frustrated with the class , helping the clients to loose weight , treat cervical , back pain , High Blood Pressure , doing pranayam , kapal bhati , yogasanas , aunty sleeping in shav asana and snoring , doing jel neti  , enjoying aerobics with friends , eating out after classes , so much more about the gym freaks , workout freaks , 
Do Share it with everyone, Comment your fav part and like krdena Video guys.. Subscribe the Channel for more amazing videos . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family  .. Comment down your Fav Part,

snippet.title: മഴപെയ്യുമ്പോൾ ചളി നിറയുന്ന വീടായിരുന്നു എന്റേത് | @jasminjaffar | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
ജീവിതത്തിൽ ഒരുപാട് വെല്ലുവിളികൾ നേരിട്ട് ഇന്ന് അറിയപ്പെടുന്ന ഒരു influencer ആയി സോഷ്യൽ മീഡിയയിൽ നിറഞ്ഞു നിൽക്കുന്ന ജാസ്മിൻ ജാഫർ അന്ന് ജോഷ് Talks ഇൽ  തനറെ ജീവിതകഥ പറയുന്നത്. 

ജാസ്മിൻ ജാഫർ തന്റെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ ഒരുപാട് വെല്ലുവിളികളും ബുദ്ധിമുട്ടുകളും തരണം ചെയ്ത് നിരവധി ആളുകൾക്ക് പ്രചോദനമായി മാറിയ സ്വാധീനശക്തിയാണ്. 

ജാസ്മിന്റെ ആദ്യകാല ജീവിതം നിരവധി പോരാട്ടങ്ങളും തിരിച്ചടികളും നിറഞ്ഞതായിരുന്നു. പരിമിതമായ സാമ്പത്തിക സ്രോതസ്സുള്ള ഒരു കുടുംബത്തിലാണ് അവൾ ജനിച്ച് വളർന്നത്, അവളുടെ മാതാപിതാക്കൾ പലപ്പോഴും ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ രണ്ടറ്റങ്ങളും കൂട്ടിമുട്ടിക്കാൻ കഷ്ടപെട്ടിരുന്നു.

ജാസ്മിൻ ജാഫർ അവിശ്വസനീയമാംവിധം സ്വാധീനിക്കുകയും ജീവിതത്തിൽ പോരാടുന്ന എല്ലാവർക്കും പ്രചോദനവുമാണ്. പോസിറ്റീവിറ്റി, സ്ഥിരോത്സാഹം, നിശ്ചയദാർഢ്യം എന്നിവയുടെ ശക്തിയുടെ തെളിവാണ് അവളുടെ കഥ, നമ്മൾ എന്ത് വെല്ലുവിളികൾ നേരിട്ടാലും, നമ്മുടെ ലക്ഷ്യങ്ങളിൽ പ്രതിജ്ഞാബദ്ധരായാൽ അവയെ തരണം ചെയ്യാനും നമ്മുടെ സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ നേടാനും കഴിയുമെന്ന് ഇത് കാണിക്കുന്നു.

Jasmin Jaffer, who has faced a lot of challenges in her life and is a popular influencer on social media, tells her life story on Josh Talks.

Jasmine Jaffer is a remarkable force of influence who has overcome many challenges and hardships in her life and become an inspiration to many people. Jasmine's early life was filled with many struggles and setbacks. She was born and brought up in a family with limited financial resources and her parents often struggled to make ends meet.

Jasmine Jaffer is incredibly influential and an inspiration to everyone struggling in life. Her story is a testament to the power of positivity, perseverance and determination, and it shows that no matter what challenges we face, we can overcome them and achieve our dreams if we commit to our goals.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം. 

#joshtalksmalayalam  #motivation #nevergiveup

ജാസ്മിന്റെ ആദ്യകാല ജീവിതം നിരവധി പോരാട്ടങ്ങളും തിരിച്ചടികളും നിറഞ്ഞതായിരുന്നു. പരിമിതമായ സാമ്പത്തിക സ്രോതസ്സുള്ള ഒരു കുടുംബത്തിലാണ് അവൾ ജനിച്ച് വളർന്നത്, അവളുടെ മാതാപിതാക്കൾ പലപ്പോഴും ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ രണ്ടറ്റങ്ങളും കൂട്ടിമുട്ടിക്കാൻ കഷ്ടപെട്ടിരുന്നു.

ജാസ്മിൻ ജാഫർ അവിശ്വസനീയമാംവിധം സ്വാധീനിക്കുകയും ജീവിതത്തിൽ പോരാടുന്ന എല്ലാവർക്കും പ്രചോദനവുമാണ്. പോസിറ്റീവിറ്റി, സ്ഥിരോത്സാഹം, നിശ്ചയദാർഢ്യം എന്നിവയുടെ ശക്തിയുടെ തെളിവാണ് അവളുടെ കഥ, നമ്മൾ എന്ത് വെല്ലുവിളികൾ നേരിട്ടാലും, നമ്മുടെ ലക്ഷ്യങ്ങളിൽ പ്രതിജ്ഞാബദ്ധരായാൽ അവയെ തരണം ചെയ്യാനും നമ്മുടെ സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ നേടാനും കഴിയുമെന്ന് ഇത് കാണിക്കുന്നു.

Jasmin Jaffer, who has faced a lot of challenges in her life and is a popular influencer on social media, tells her life story on Josh Talks.

Jasmine Jaffer is a remarkable force of influence who has overcome many challenges and hardships in her life and become an inspiration to many people. Jasmine's early life was filled with many struggles and setbacks. She was born and brought up in a family with limited financial resources and her parents often struggled to make ends meet.

Jasmine Jaffer is incredibly influential and an inspiration to everyone struggling in life. Her story is a testament to the power of positivity, perseverance and determination, and it shows that no matter what challenges we face, we can overcome them and achieve our dreams if we commit to our goals.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

F फूल बन कर तेरे बा हो में को ई और ना खिलेगी
M तेरे का रन रहता हूँ मैं Dipration में

Namaskaara Bossu, Dedicate this song to everyone who doubts you, critisice you in your journey,
1st they laugh,
next they talk,
at last you win ❤️
This is life ❤️

After the incredible success of his hit single "Don't Worry" in 2019, All Ok, the rising star of the music industry is making a grand return with "Don't Worry 2", which promises to offer a fresh perspective on All Ok's distinctive sound. 

With a combination of captivating beats and heartfelt lyrics, "Don't Worry 2" is sure to create an unforgettable listening experience. Get ready to groove and sing along with one of the most popular artists in the industry as he delivers another exciting new release.

snippet.title: India Travel Vlog in Tamil | Alandra's Adventure in India - Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video, I am sharing some of the highlights from my recent trip to India. This was Alandra's second visit to India and this time, she had a lot of fun visiting the farm, beach, seeing all relatives and shopping. I was in India for 6 weeks and Alandra had a blast. She also had a lot of fun with cats and trying the different fruits there.
#steffiulagam #steffivlogs

Friends, hope you liked this week's vlog. While, I don't think I can do the weekly vlogs in Steffi Ulagam, I will occasionally share some of the events and interesting things in Madras Samayal. Thank you so much for your love and support.

mr.title: कांदे पोहे - कोथरूड VS सातारा । #Satara #Kothrud | #BhaDiPa
mr.description:
कोथरूडच्या आपल्या मुलीला बघायला आलंय रॉयल साताऱ्याचं स्थळ! कोथरुडकरांसाठी सातारा काही जास्त लांब नाही. ह्या वेळेस कांदेपोह्यांपासून सुरु झालेला कार्यक्रम कंदीपेढे खाऊन गोड होईल का? कोथरूड आणि सातारकरांची सोयरीक जुळेल का? जाणून घेण्यासाठी विडिओ शेवटपर्यंत पहा. 

कास्ट:
लीना भागवत
भाग्यश्री लिमये
रोहित माने
संतोष पाटील

श्रेयावली:
दिग्दर्शक - अक्षय नर
लेखक - सुमित पाटील
सिनेमॅटोग्राफर - अजिंक्य खडपेकर
ध्वनी - सनी
संकलक - करिष्मा दळवी
सहाय्यक दिग्दर्शक - सार्थक चिरनेरकर
कलरिस्ट - अजिंक्य खडपेकर
प्रोडक्शन हेड - केदार नायडू
प्रोडक्शन कॉर्डिनेटर  - अक्षय गोपाळ
प्रोग्रामिंग हेड आणि मार्केटिंग स्ट्रॅटेजिस्ट - प्राची हंकारे आणि अक्षय नर
क्रिएटिव्हस् - अनिकेत जाधव, नदीम खान
स्पॉट - एकेंद्र सिंग
लाईट - किसन
सेल्स आणि ब्रँड सोल्युशन्स हेड - स्वानंद तेंडुलकर
सेल्स एक्झिक्युटिव्ह - शिल्पा शेट्ये
सेल्स असोसिएट - चिन्मय जाधव
सोशल मीडिया टीम - श्वेता धाडवे, प्राची बागवे, तेजस देसाई
उपशीर्षके - अमेय राणे
इक्विपमेंट्स - रेड आय इक्विपमेंट्स

snippet.title: Chengiz Official Hindi Teaser | Jeet | Susmita | Rohit Roy | Shataf | Neeraj Pandey | Rajesh Ganguly
snippet.description:
‘Chengiz’ has officially set foot.
Get ready for an action-packed experience as we unveil the Hindi Teaser of #Chengiz. The story of an underworld don whose grip on the city is unbreakable. This is the very first time a Bengali film is set to release in Hindi simultaneously. So, mark your calendars and get ready to enter the dark, mysterious world of the underworld, with us!

Screenplay, Dialogue & Direction : Rajesh Ganguly 
Story : Neeraj Pandey & Rajesh Ganguly 
Produced by JEET, Gopal Madnani & Amit Jumrani 
D.O.P : Manas Ganguly

Action Director : Stunt Silva

Make up : Somnath Kundu, Arjun Das

snippet.title: Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? IN NEWS | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Today’s InNews PDF Telegram Link: https://t.me/innewsdrishtiias

Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? 

Congress leader Rahul Gandhi has been disqualified from the Lok Sabha, a day after he was convicted in a defamation case by a Surat court. A notice issued by the Lok Sabha Secretariat said he stood disqualified from the House from March 23, the day of his conviction. Rahul Gandhi has to now move a higher court and get his conviction stayed. Chief Judicial Magistrate HH Verma convicted Gandhi in a 2019 defamation case, for saying ‘why do all thieves have the name Modi’, and sentenced him to two years in prison. The remarks were made during a rally in Kolar, Karnataka, in the run-up to the 2019 Lok Sabha elections. “Why do all thieves, be it Nirav Modi, Lalit Modi or Narendra Modi, have Modi in their names,” Gandhi had said in Hindi.

localized.title: Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? IN NEWS | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Today’s InNews PDF Telegram Link: https://t.me/innewsdrishtiias

Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? 

Congress leader Rahul Gandhi has been disqualified from the Lok Sabha, a day after he was convicted in a defamation case by a Surat court. A notice issued by the Lok Sabha Secretariat said he stood disqualified from the House from March 23, the day of his conviction. Rahul Gandhi has to now move a higher court and get his conviction stayed. Chief Judicial Magistrate HH Verma convicted Gandhi in a 2019 defamation case, for saying ‘why do all thieves have the name Modi’, and sentenced him to two years in prison. The remarks were made during a rally in Kolar, Karnataka, in the run-up to the 2019 Lok Sabha elections. “Why do all thieves, be it Nirav Modi, Lalit Modi or Narendra Modi, have Modi in their names,” Gandhi had said in Hindi.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 26 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

Our guest for this episode is a Celebrated Journalist, Managing Editor, Firstpost and award-winning Indian news anchor Palki Sharma in conversation with Ranveer Allahbadia - A conversation touching a broad spectrum of topics. Underlying the importance of self-acceptance, this podcast will nudge you on the road to introspection.

In this podcast, we spoke about the different media narratives, the representation of journalism, her Interview with Perez Musharraf, China's war with Taiwan, the future of Pakistan & so much more.

India's Top Journalist Palki Sharma on News & Media, its representation & geopolitics. Hope you enjoy this lovely chat. 

(0:00) - Ranveer x Palki Sharma Begins
(4:05) - Media narratives in India
(10:00) - How are Indian journalists represented?
(15:27) - Interview with Perez Musharraf
(21:40) - China's secrets of progress
(30:40) - China's war with Taiwan?
(38:20) - What is the future of Pakistan?
(42:17) - Her commentary on the USA
(50:22) - Why emotion can overpower data?
(53:15) - Thank you for watching

#journalism #palkisharma

snippet.title: 20 Wheat Atta in India Ranked from Worst to Best
snippet.description:
Which is the best wheat flour in the Indian market? One food that a majority of India eats on a daily basis is atta. But which one do you use? Aashirwaad? Fortune? Patanjali? MP Sharbati atta? Organic or multigrain? What about the local chakki atta?  What do the reports say when 10 leading brands of wheat flour were tested? To put it simply, which is the best atta in the Indian market?

Buy Mamaearth Toxin Free Mineral Based Sunscreen - https://bit.ly/3XXlNtY
(Apply code FITTUBER21 to get 21% off)
Buy from Amazon - https://amzn.to/3JPNu3a

For this video, I not only bought and carefully went through the ingredients and nutritional information of the wheat flours made by the most popular brands but also to delve deeper into the subject, I got in touch with various food experts. I met local flour mill owners and also got the opportunity to talk to wheat-growing farmers. Some of the things that came before me were shocking. Although one thing is for sure that watching this video, you will have a clear idea as to which atta you should buy. On the basis of my research, I have categorized all the atta available in the Indian market into 5 categories.

04:42 - Category 2 - This one is intensively marketed as superior atta. But is it? Not really.

07:16 - Category 4 - Is organic wheat flour any good? It is definitely priced high.

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 27 Teaser - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#yumnazaidi 
#wahajali

snippet.title: *I FINALLY moved into my new apartment* 🏡 || VLOG
snippet.description:
Hello,
Last few days before we move into my new apartment...! It's been hectic, with the pregnancy and so many decisions to be taken, I'm just grateful to be healthy and waking up in my new house every day now. 

Can't wait to get back to normalcy and routine, I need to focus on the baby and my birth now.

Thank you for coming with me on this Journey, it's the end of an era but it's the beginning of a new book in my life. 
I love you
Xx

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3727 - 24 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3727: Rickshaw Kahan Hain?
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha gets swooned by Babita's traditional dressing style and offers her a ride. Fortunately, Babita Ji was also attending the function at her friend's place, which happens to be near Jetha's shop, so she accepted the offer. Popatlal objects to Jetha stating that only three people could ride in an auto rickshaw so Taarak suggests that they should take a cab. Jetha is already anxious about his meeting with Ramsong's Area Manager, Mr. Rustom, who happens to be very punctual, but he also cannot miss the chance to commute alongside Babita Ji. Will Jetha be able to attend the meeting or is there a new trouble hovering? 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3727, 24 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000214631

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 25 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 25 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 22nd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

snippet.title: SITTA SITTENDA KOTTE PART 4 FULL SONG | PARSHURAM NAGAM | SINGER LAVANYA | BODDU DILIP
snippet.description:
SITTA SITTENDA KOTTE PART 4 FULL SONG | PARSHURAM NAGAM | SINGER LAVANYA | BODDU DILIP


రచన&దర్శకత్వం: పరశురాం నాగం
సంగీతం: కాయితోజు ప్రవీణ్ కుమార్
గానం: లావణ్య & బొడ్డు దిలీప్ కుమార్
ట్యూన్ సోర్స్: నరావుల మల్లవ్వ
DOP: హరీష్ పటేల్
ఎడిటింగ్: ఆదర్శ్ పటేల్
నటీనటులు: కార్తిక్ రెడ్డి, మానస,
బిట్టు , హనీ, 
సహనటులు:
పల్లవి, పరశురాం నాగం, 
గంగ శ్రీకాంత్ మాస్టర్
టెక్నికల్ సపోర్ట్: వంశీ S

PRODUCTION: 
MANAIR MUSIC AND MOVIES

ప్రత్యేక ధన్యవాదాలు:
LADDU MUSIC, VIVAAN
ONE TECHNOLOGIES,
వాగ్దేవీ కళాశాల, వేములవాడ
విజేత ఆర్థ్రో హాస్పిటల్, వేములవాడ
RB శరత్ రాజా , వేములవాడ


ప్రత్యేక ధన్యవాదాలు:
నాగం కొమురయ్య మల్లవ్వ
నాగం మౌనిక బాలశేఖర్
గుంటి నరేష్,
అభి, జగిత్యాల
తొంటి లస్మయ్య & ఫ్యామిలీ
పెంటల మహాంకాళి & ఫ్యామిలీ
కోరే దేవయ్య & ఫ్యామిలీ
జమున -తిరుపతి & ఫ్యామిలీ
జోగాపూర్ గ్రామస్తులు & వేములవాడ పురప్రముఖులు


పాట నేపథ్యం:
తలిదండ్రులు తమ పిల్లల్ని  ఎంతో అల్లారు ముద్దుగా... స్కూల్ బస్ లో.. బడికి పంపిస్తారు. 
కానీ.. బస్ డ్రైవర్ ఫోన్ మాట్లాడుతూ ఉంటాడు. ఆ పక్కనే ఐస్ క్రీం ఉంటుంది. దాన్నీ చూసి.. పిల్లాడు ఉరికి వస్తాడు. బస్ వెనక్కి వస్తూండడంతో.. బస్ కింద పడి.. కాలు విరుగుతుంది. అది చూసి అక్క వెనక్కి పరిగెత్తుకుంటు రావడంతో.. తొక్కుడు బండ మీద జారి తల పగులుతుంది. జీవచ్చవాళ్ల ఉన్న పిల్లల్ని చూసి అమ్మానాన్నలు గుండె పగులుతుంది. వెంటనే హాస్పిటల్ కి ఎత్తుకుపోతారు. 
అక్కడ డాక్టర్ గారు చెకప్ చేసి... ఆపరేషన్ చేసి.. బతికిస్తారు. దాంతో.. ఆందరి మొఖాలు ఆనందతాండవం చేస్తాయి.
కథ సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది అనే లోపే... కాలు విరిగి కట్టుతో ఉన్న... పిలవాన్ని తోటి పిల్లలు.. ఆడుకోవడానికి రానివ్వరు. దాంతో పిల్లవాడు బాగా బాధపడతాడు. 
అది గమనించి.. తలిదండ్రులు.. అక్కున చేర్చుకోని ఓదార్చుతారు. మెల్లగా నడకలు నేర్పిస్తారు. అలా అలా కొద్దిరోజుల్లో పిల్లలిద్దరూ సాధారణ స్థితికి వస్తారు. 
మెల్లగా.. జాగ్రత్తగా బడికి వెళ్లడం ప్రారంభిస్తారు. 

దాంతో కథ పరిపూర్ణంగా సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది. మా ఈ ప్రయత్నం మీకు నచ్చితే.. plz Support చేయండి.. షేర్ చేయండి. ధన్యవాదాలు..
మీ పరశురాం నాగం.✍️
రచయిత & దర్శకులు.
MANAIR MUSIC & MOVIES

కానీ.. బస్ డ్రైవర్ ఫోన్ మాట్లాడుతూ ఉంటాడు. ఆ పక్కనే ఐస్ క్రీం ఉంటుంది. దాన్నీ చూసి.. పిల్లాడు ఉరికి వస్తాడు. బస్ వెనక్కి వస్తూండడంతో.. బస్ కింద పడి.. కాలు విరుగుతుంది. అది చూసి అక్క వెనక్కి పరిగెత్తుకుంటు రావడంతో.. తొక్కుడు బండ మీద జారి తల పగులుతుంది. జీవచ్చవాళ్ల ఉన్న పిల్లల్ని చూసి అమ్మానాన్నలు గుండె పగులుతుంది. వెంటనే హాస్పిటల్ కి ఎత్తుకుపోతారు. 
అక్కడ డాక్టర్ గారు చెకప్ చేసి... ఆపరేషన్ చేసి.. బతికిస్తారు. దాంతో.. ఆందరి మొఖాలు ఆనందతాండవం చేస్తాయి.
కథ సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది అనే లోపే... కాలు విరిగి కట్టుతో ఉన్న... పిలవాన్ని తోటి పిల్లలు.. ఆడుకోవడానికి రానివ్వరు. దాంతో పిల్లవాడు బాగా బాధపడతాడు. 
అది గమనించి.. తలిదండ్రులు.. అక్కున చేర్చుకోని ఓదార్చుతారు. మెల్లగా నడకలు నేర్పిస్తారు. అలా అలా కొద్దిరోజుల్లో పిల్లలిద్దరూ సాధారణ స్థితికి వస్తారు. 
మెల్లగా.. జాగ్రత్తగా బడికి వెళ్లడం ప్రారంభిస్తారు. 

దాంతో కథ పరిపూర్ణంగా సుఖాంతం అవుతుంది. మా ఈ ప్రయత్నం మీకు నచ్చితే.. plz Support చేయండి.. షేర్ చేయండి. ధన్యవాదాలు..
మీ పరశురాం నాగం.✍️

snippet.title: BIG ICE CREAM | Biggest Stick ice making | Watermelon ice | Kiwi ice | Milk ice | Fruit ice Making
snippet.description:
In our childhood, we enjoy those moments with tasting stick ice. We call this ice "Kuchi ice". Today in our village, we made the three most giant colorful stick ice with fruits and milk. We made three types of ice cream. The first one is milk. The second is watermelon. The third one is Kiwi.

Childhood memory comes again! Tasty!

snippet.title: Hyundai Verna SX(O) Turbo 2023- ₹17 lakh | Real-life review
snippet.description:
Namaste friends, please LIKE & SUBSCRIBE :)

The Hyundai Verna, or Hyundai Accent is a subcompact car produced by Hyundai. In Australia, the first generation models carried over the Hyundai Excel name used by the Accent's predecessor. On 13 February 2023, Hyundai released the sixth-generation model as the Verna (BN7) in India on 21 March 2023, featuring Hyundai's 'Sensuous Sportiness' design identity. Its design is inspired by the Elantra. With a total of 17 Level 2 - ADAS features, the all-new Hyundai VERNA creates a new precedent for this segment with Hyundai SmartSense. Further, with this segment’s best in class acoustic experience - Bose Premium Sound 8 Speaker system. #HyundaiVerna #Verna #Hyundai

Petrol: 1497 cc, Inline-4 cylinder, Hyundai Smartstream G1.5 MPi engine, 113 HP Power, 143 Nm Torque, 18 kmpl (Manual), 19 kmpl (Automatic) Average, 45 litre Fuel Tank, 6-speed Manual or IVT Automatic Transmission

Petrol: 1482 cc, Inline-4 cylinder, Hyundai Smartstream G1.5T Turbo GDi engine, 157 HP Power, 253 Nm Torque, 20 kmpl Average, 45 litre Fuel Tank, 6-speed Manual or 7-speed DCT Automatic Transmission

7 Colours: Grey, Tellurian Brown, Silver, Red, White, Black, Starry Night (Roof colour- Black)

7 Variants: EX, S, SX, SX(O), SX Turbo, SX(O) Turbo, SX(O) Turbo DCT

3 Upholsteries: Fabric, Beige Leatherette, Black Leatherette

4 Wheels: 15 inch Steel, 15 inch Alloy, 16 inch Diamond Cut Alloy, 16 inch Black Alloy

Price range: Rs. 10.89 lakh - Rs. 17.37 lakh (Ex-showroom, Delhi)

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

Kitni khoobsoorat hogi
Teri meri prem kahani ,
Sang mein budhe honge hum
Sang mein beetegi jawaani

Kitni khoobsoorat hogi
Teri meri prem kahani ,
Sang mein budhe honge hum
Sang mein beetegi jawaani

Mujhko lagta hai
Teri bahon me kuch jadu tona hai ,
Main toh tha mitti
mujhko tune chuu ke kar dia Sona hai !

Tum zarori hurdam ho
Hume har pal sath me rehna hai ,
Hasna hai Hume tere sath me
Tere sath me rona hai !

Aur baaki saari baatein tumko hi seekhani hogi
Roti main paka dunga par tumhe
Hath se khilani hogi !

Teri meri prem kahani ,
Sang mein bhudhe honge hum
Sang mein beetegi jawani !

Haa bachchon ke jaise karunga mai ,

Kuch bhi karunga mai !

aansu na mai aane dunga
Aankho me tere ,
Roz tujhko sulaunga
Mere gaane ga ke re !

Mehndi mere naam ki tujhko
Hathon me lagani hogi ,
Subah shaam aur raatein
Tere sath hi suhani hongi !

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3726 - 23 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3726: Tapu Sena Ki Safalta
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena's creative contribution is mentioned by Asit Kumarr Modi, who announces a foreign trip for them. In the midst of this, Popatlal raises his voice and protests. He expresses his dissatisfaction with Asit Kumarr Modi's failure to take his wedding seriously. Asit Ji promises Popatlal that he will find him a suitable bride soon. Later, the residents of Gokuldham celebrate the occasion with dancing and good food. The following morning, Bapuji seeks help from the Tapu Sena to install the game on his phone. Bhide also expresses gratitude to Tapu Sena. Bhide and Madhavi present Tapu Sena with a box of ladoo to express their compliments. Meanwhile. Jetha worries about his meeting with Ramsong dealers. Stay tuned for more details!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3726, 23 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000214537

He expresses his dissatisfaction with Asit Kumarr Modi's failure to take his wedding seriously. Asit Ji promises Popatlal that he will find him a suitable bride soon. Later, the residents of Gokuldham celebrate the occasion with dancing and good food. The following morning, Bapuji seeks help from the Tapu Sena to install the game on his phone. Bhide also expresses gratitude to Tapu Sena. Bhide and Madhavi present Tapu Sena with a box of ladoo to express their compliments. Meanwhile. Jetha worries about his meeting with Ramsong dealers. Stay tuned for more details!

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3726, 23 Mar 2023

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Rahul Disqualification: राहुल गांधी की संसद सदस्यता रद्द,क्या बोले विपक्ष के ये 4 नेता?  (BBC Hindi)
snippet.description:
संसद की सदस्यता रद्द होने के बाद कांग्रेस नेता राहुल गांधी ने प्रतिक्रिया दी है. उन्होंने ट्विटर पर लिखा है, "मैं भारत की आवाज़ के लिए लड़ रहा हूं. मैं हर कीमत चुकाने को तैयार हूं." राहुल गांधी की संसद सदस्यता रद्द होने पर विपक्ष के नेता भी नाराज़ दिखे. वहीं बीजेपी इस फ़ैसले को सही ठहराती दिख रही है. देखिए वीडियो

#rahulgandhi #disqualification #parliament 

* जिन खबरों, तस्वीरों और दावों पर आपको हो शक, हम आपके लिए करेंगे उनकी परख. बीबीसी फ़ैक्ट चेक है आपके साथ. बस भेजिए WhatsApp मैसेज 9811520111 पर. बीबीसी फ़ैक्ट चेक यानी सच की कसौटी.

* Corona Virus से जुड़े और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=npgvIvfmNkE&list=PLYxuvEJLss6ByutcqkthikPxV3ccUkwPB

* कोरोना वायरस से जुड़ी सारी प्रामाणिक ख़बरें पढ़ने के लिए क्लिक करें : https://www.bbc.com/hindi/international-51848794

* ऐसे ही और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

* बीबीसी हिंदी से आप इन सोशल मीडिया चैनल्स पर भी जुड़ सकते हैं-

फ़ेसबुक- https://www.facebook.com/BBCnewsHindi
ट्विटर- https://twitter.com/BBCHindi
इंस्टाग्राम- https://www.instagram.com/bbchindi/

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.
